DELIVERABILITY DISCLAIMER
=========================
FallList sends email via third-party mailer APIs (Resend, Postmark, Mailgun,
SendGrid). Deliverability depends entirely on:
- Your sender domain SPF/DKIM/DMARC configuration
- Your mailer account standing with the provider
- Your list quality (engagement rates, unsubscribe handling, complaint rates)
- Recipient mailbox provider policies

The authors of FallList accept no liability for emails not delivered,
classified as spam, or for any account suspensions by your chosen mailer
provider. Follow standard email-sending best practices: verify your domain,
respect unsubscribes, and never email purchased lists.
